HEADWORD: Noteless
<hw>Note"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not attracting notice; not
conspicuous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Noteless</qex> as the race from which he sprung.</q>
